channel.title: I Cant Log onto a online server
channel.description: Well I bet alot of people ask this but i just downloaded moparscape 3.0 yesterday and i have been satisfied playing by myself.... but now i am wondering how i can get online? I try to get online but it always says "server must be down" so i try another and it never works. if some 1 can please help me i would really apprieciate it thanks. :D

item.title: I Cant Log onto a online server
item.dc:creator: @udluv2 udluv2
item.description:
@udluv2 wrote:

u have to download hamachi and then connext to their server on their and then open up moparscape click file>new server and enter their i.p.

Then if they got a port click file>new port and enter there port.

Then click enter and enter ur username and pass then press enter.

Viola your playing with people
